name: CrystalFang Mystic Grove Squirrel
text: Beneath the moon's quiet watch, CrystalFang, heir to Whiskerfang's legacy, cradled the Diamond Acorn. The Mystic Grove murmured tales of Whiskerfang's bravery, inspiring CrystalFang's own vigil. With sabers sparking starlight, he bound toward destiny's embrace, guardian of the grove, shield against the encroaching silence of an unknown darkness.
